						               													<description>Sconudi playing cards are a unique, new set of cards that can play multiple card games.  Sconudi Playing Cards have four parts: shapes, colors, numbers, and directions. There are 50 cards in each deck. most games can be played with 2 to 4 players.  Also, there are solitaire games to play alone.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Currently there are nine published games that can be played with Sconudi playing cards:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Chainbreaker&amp;#10;Ages 7 &amp;amp; up&amp;#10;2-4 players&amp;#10;Follow the flow of arrows on the cards and score the Chainbreaker!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Continuity&amp;#10;Ages 7 &amp;amp; up&amp;#10;2-4 players&amp;#10;Attempt to draw a five-card hand in which each card has two matching characteristics (shapes, color, numbers, directions) as the cards immediately adjacent to it!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Mimic&amp;#10;Ages 7 &amp;amp; up&amp;#10;2-4 players &amp;#10;Score points by matching as many characteristics (shapes, color, numbers, directions) while also playing the highest number card!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Pinwheel Solitaire&amp;#10;NEW!&amp;#10;Ages 7 &amp;amp; up&amp;#10;1 player&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Recall&amp;#10;Ages 5 &amp;amp; up&amp;#10;1-4 players &amp;#10;Find the hidden match or hidden numbers sequence by turning over hidden cards!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Sconudi Poker&amp;#10;New hands! New hand ranks! Play the classic in a complete new way!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Sconudi Tennis&amp;#10;Ages 7 &amp;amp; up&amp;#10;2 players&amp;#10;Play the highest hidden card of your hand to win the volley!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Sconudi Trump&amp;#10;Ages 7 &amp;amp; up&amp;#10;2-4 players&amp;#10;Play the highest card of the selected trump to win the hand!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Straight Solitaire&amp;#10;NEW!&amp;#10;Ages 7 &amp;amp; up&amp;#10;1 player&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
